\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 The ebbs and flows of the ferry boat lulls him in his reluctant sleep,}{ Weeks of relentless study had taken its toll on him. His hair was more unkempt than usual, tufts sticking up where he\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92d run his fingers through it in frustration. Heavy shadows under his  eyes indicates the sleepless nights chasing formulas and theories. He blinked hard, fighting the pull of sleep as the tram jolted over another bump. }
\par\pard\plain \ltrch\loch {On his lap lay a dishevelled pile of notes. Some in precise, orderly handwriting, others in his own frantic scrawl. It\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s barely legible after feverish study sessions. Intricate alchemical diagrams spiralled across the pages like cryptic secrets. Each symbol is a lifeline connecting him to an Alchemist\u8217\'92s teachings. He clutched them tightly, a bridge between himself and the elusive mastery of alchemy he could almost feel slipping through his tired fingers. }
